          будь-яких працівників або консультантів Замовника.
    %tr
      %td.padding_top_11
        %p.bold 9. Legal Relationship.
        %p
          Except to the extent specifically required under the terms of this agreement, Consultant shall not
          be deemed an agent or employee of Customer and may not represent itself as having any authority to
          act on behalf of Customer without Customer's prior written consent. This agreement shall not be
          interpreted as establishing anything other than a consultant relationship and no partnership,
